snippet.title: Around the Sun with Maureen Van Zandt, François Clemmons and Brad Forenza Episode #90
snippet.description: We have made it around the sun one more time, and to kick off its 3rd AMAZING season, Amber Live! is bringing together some unlikely forces in entertianment. Actor Brad Forenza has created a series called Around The Sun, and in it he has a multitude of incredible talent, including Maureen Van Zandt and François Clemmons!  "Around the Sun" is a scripted, episodic podcast that explores human connections, made and missed, with an existential New York flare. Whether consumed together or independently, the comedy, tragedy, and soul of Around the Sun embraces one character’s assertion that, “We’re never alone in New York… even if it feels like the opposite is often true.”  Don't miss this fantastic journey Around the Sun!
